  "text": "The Czech Republic has for a long time been included among those European Union States with a high share of mobile networks traffic. It is just forecasting of the mobile networks traffic volumes, in the interconnection services (national and international services) in particular, what this study is dealing with. Mobile phone services and mobile phones, in particular in Indonesia, were analysed by [CITATION_1] .",
